parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe>.Sending the boy to my dressing room, Paul?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.Take a seat next to Andrea, 1Hero. The sooner we start, the sooner we finish.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx>.You’re looking sharp. Relax and trust your instincts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Talk about charisma. This town’s going to eat you right up, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp>.I knew you had it in you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaOp.Alright, let’s review the footage and get it to editing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Careful, 1Hero. You can’t leave any doubt in the public’s mind.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.You’ve implied that something could still happen here. We have to assure the public that they are safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.But what about Duncan and Charles? Shouldn’t we hedge our bets just a little?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I need to be able to trust you, 1Hero. We have a narrative to maintain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.You can’t give people any seeds of doubt or rumors will run wild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.You have one message, 1Hero: North Santiva is safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I won’t mention anything about Charles or Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Your role is now public relations. I want you focused on keeping the people calm.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can handle this, Andrea. You can count on me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Now, don’t forget to turn up the charm for Miss Foxx.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.Without her alliance, our message will quickly break and a cycle of paranoia will stoke the fires of this news organization.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.She only cares about content. Keep her on our side and keep your lips sealed regarding anything having to do with North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.This job will be easy if you make it easy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrOp.We’re all good. The segment will make a perfect addition to this evening’s news.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.I can’t wait to watch it tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.If you don’t mind, I’ll be heading back to the station now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Come on, 1Hero. Let’s chat back in the changing room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrOp.So how long are we thinking before you make arrests?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrE^x.Soon, Paul. And when we do you’ll be the first person we call.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Great job, 1Hero. You’re sure to capture the hearts of the viewers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrOp.So you think this broadcast will lure them out?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx^.The Guild thieves should believe they have a head start and should feel the pressure to find the painting first…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.This is going to be big. People love art heists.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.Hell yeah they do. This could give us news for weeks…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp^.Don’t worry, Paul. We’ll have plenty to give you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrOp.So what’s the name of the painting?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.Not yet. Let’s plan another interview next week.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx^.If you’ll excuse me, I must head home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp^.You know I always come through, Paul.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlHaOp.Great job, you two! People are loving Detective Canmore. A true model detective for our community to look up to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.Alright. Enough praise. Let him get back to work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFlOp.And, 1Hero. We’ll keep our little secret close to the chest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.We’ll play Kimura’s game, but we want more.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.If you get caught, I’ll deny everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll get that transmitter fixed. This case goes deeper than the Eclipse Guild and I want to know what’s happening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.You bend the rules, 1Hero. You should be working here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I think I’ll keep kissing up to Andrea and maybe one day I’ll be commissioner myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlHaEx^.Just in time. We go live in five minutes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoOp^.Our jobs are on the line. If this doesn’t go well, we’re fired.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.You took down the Guild. They won’t fire you after this broadcast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx.Get your story straight, you two. We’re going live.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaEx^.Get seated. We go live in thirty seconds.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlHaOp^.Cut! And we’re done with the live coverage.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoOp^.Andrea isn’t going to like that last part about the undercover agents.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlHaEx^.That’s a wrap, everyone. Thanks for staying late.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx^.I’m going to take off. I’ll see you bright and early tomorrow, Kimberly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Not sure why the commissioner would fire you after this…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Seems you’ve earned a raise, if you ask me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Listen, Kimberly. I don’t know how many more interviews we’ll have…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Andrea really wants the Guild case put behind us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.She looks bad with everything coming out. But she can’t sweep it under the rug.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp^.You’re going to stay on this story?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.I have a feeling it will… evolve.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.We’re not used to going live before the evening segment. This was a special case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFrOp^.Thanks for doing this, Miss Foxx. It means a lot to us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.You should come back, Melissa. You’ve got a look for TV.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Dress her up nice and sexy next time, Kimberly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.No rush, Melissa. We have the place to ourselves…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.There’s not much more to say. The interrogation went cold.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Enough Guild talk. I want to know if you two have fucked yet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Oh, come on. 1Hero fucks anything with a pussy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Gross. Don’t make me think about it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.You’re missing out, Melissa. This boy’s cock is heaven.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlEx^.Be careful. His head can only get so big before it bursts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.You like this big head of mine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe^.You drive me crazy. But perhaps you’ve grown on me… a tad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoCl^.Shit!... Tell me no one saw that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.As much as I’d love to stay for pillow talk, I’m needed elsewhere.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.What are you going to do about Andrea?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ll deal with whatever comes my way… But maybe with some luck, I’ll be back at work tomorrow.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe^.It’s too quiet without someone to annoy me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.But I might be able to pick the lock with the right tool.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.My lock pick is too weak for this one. I need something stronger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Maybe I can use my lock pick to open it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Too bad we don’t have time to set up crucifixes in the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlDe.Don’t worry, 1Hero. I’m packing a big one right here for them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She’s with Kimberly… They stole my amulet!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaOp^.Are you talking about the amulets in the book?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Judy and Kimberly stole one of the amulets that can destroy Lilith.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.Where are they? Where did they go?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I couldn’t chase them… I was handcuffed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaOp.If you want to stop Lilith, you’ll need three amulets… ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.They are taking the amulets to Lillian… She’s collecting them so no one can use them on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.So you’re saying we need to get these amulets back?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Clearly, she doesn’t want us to have them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp^.1Hero? What the hell is going on here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx^.Turns out you’re not lying. We’re digging up some major dirt at the station as we speak.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp^.You tried to break into the warehouse… Who the hell are you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.I’ve got other matters to attend to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx^.No one’s going anywhere. We have this place locked down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnOp.Officer!? Where the hell are you going? We need to talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe^.Great… Now we have to deal with the cops.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnEx.We can handle this on our own.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.We’re in over our heads. We need their help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.I can handle demons, but I’d certainly feel even safer with some armed men around here too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe^.Where the hell is Miss Foxx? Is she going to broadcast or not?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe.Father Solomon tells me that Madalyn didn’t come out of the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe.If they’re making their big play, why isn’t she a part of it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It’s a lot to explain, Paul. But trust me, it’ll be over soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "GnAnEx.The Toma is ours. You are only delaying the inevitable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaEx^.I couldn’t let him take her body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx^.Quick! Burn the shell bodies before the demons come back for them!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoCl.You want us to burn the bodies?... Right now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx^.Erica has been sent to Limbo. I am Arianna, an angel of God.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.How do we save her? How do we save Erica’s soul?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaEx^.I’m afraid her soul will be judged… She won’t be returning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaAgNo1.We have to stop her! We have to kill her!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Arianna… Can you help us destroy her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx^.Lilith is more powerful than I am… But we have the Lord on our side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.What about Erica? Did she have the Lord on her side, too?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You told me the path was being laid out for me… That I would be doing God’s will.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m going back to Hell and I’m going to kill Lilith.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeWoOp.What the hell happened? Where is Kimberly?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.We stopped the broadcast… but she got away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.What the hell were these Guild goons trying to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.What the hell were these Guild goons trying to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She'll be okay... It's hard to explain, but she'll be fine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaDe.Our interviewees for the sex segment should be here any moment now…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrOp.Such a pleasure to see you again. It’s been a long time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.Let me introduce you to Kimberly Foxx, our star anchor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp>.It’s good to meet you, Ms. Bancroft. I look forward to our interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrOp.Likewise, Ms. Foxx. I hope this interview goes better than last time I was here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.And, as a bonus, we happen to have with us today North Santiva’s celebrity detective, 1Hero Canmore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.Detective, let me introduce you to Amanda Bancroft, the CEO of Sensular Labs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrOp^.It’s a pleasure to meet you, Detective Canmore. You’re quite famous.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOpNo3.Haha, I guess so. Your love potion has been making headlines, too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFlOp^.Have you tried it? It’ll rock your socks off.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDeNo4.Honestly, I’ve only tried the competing brand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmAnDe^.Seems my competition has a deal with this town.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiFrCl.Is this equipment built to standard? Where are the permits for the cameras?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiFlDe.So a detective, huh? I have some experience with guns myself, you know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiFrDe.And I know a thing or two about security. I learned from the best!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiAnDe.I smell a trap… This better not be another news segment on that old ESU sex scandal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrDe^.I’m sure Paul knows why we are here, and it’s not to talk about the past.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.Well, it’s about time for the interview. So if you don’t mind, Ms. Bancroft, right this way…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmWoOp^.Paul, can you make sure security keeps him company? There’s no telling what he’ll get up to on his own.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaDe.I’m sorry, Ms. Bancroft, but our security is too busy to look after… an adult?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrOp^.Make sure my son doesn’t hurt himself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.1Hero, please. We’re all friends here, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp^.Come on, 1Hero. It’s just for a little while.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmWoDe^.If left to his own devices, there’s no telling what my son will get up to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.But you owe me for this, Kim.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Come on, Simon. How about we go make sure the building is secure, or something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiHaAg.Oh, yeah? I know all about that! Buddy taught me everything he knew about security!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiFrEx.Don’t worry, Detective Canmore! I’ve got this!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmAnOp^.What am I going to do with that boy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx.It’s time for the interview, Ms. Bancroft.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnEx.1Hero, what are you doing? We’re live! Go find Simon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnEx.I’m a bit busy right now, as you can see. Shouldn’t you be looking after that Bancroft kid?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrEx>.… and that’s what my company and our product is all about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.But I think a lot of our viewers want to know more about a certain rumor going around…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Some say your company’s product is what’s responsible for the so-called sex virus outbreak.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrOp>.I assure you and your viewers that my company has nothing to do with the sex virus.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaOp.You must admit that it’s a strange coincidence, the sex virus outbreak happening just as your love potion becomes popular.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnEx.But isn’t it true that information came out that your company is under investigation by law enforcement?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFlEx>.Some people just want to find a scapegoat for their own incompetence.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmBaOp>.The truth is that no one knows where it came from.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrEx>.When it comes down to it, I’m just a successful businesswoman selling an amazing product that brings a lot of people happiness.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.And what a product it is. I can personally vouch for it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Ms. Bancroft, thank you for coming today. I’m sure our viewers appreciated hearing directly from you about some of their concerns.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFrOp>.It has been my pleasure, Ms. Foxx. Thank you for having me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.Alright, folks, that’s the end of our interview with Ms. Bancroft. I’m Kimberly Foxx, Channel 4 News…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaOp.Coming up after the break we take you into labs working directly with the virus. Could a lab leak explain everything?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.We would love to have you on again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmFlOp^.Thank you, Kimberly. I'll admit, you’re a better interviewer than Harrison.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.I mean… No need to make comparisons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaOp^.We’ve got a prerecorded investigation into the origin of the sex virus rolling. Be back in twenty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrDe^.No, but it doesn’t matter. Everyone wants to know where it came from, so it’ll bring in a lot of viewers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx^.Viewers that will keep watching afterwards to see everyone’s favorite detective.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Now how about that favor you owe me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I recall this couch being pretty comfortable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.How ‘bout we get really comfortable on it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOpNo3.Hahaha, you’re so bad. But we can’t do anything with that dweeb looking on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmAnAg^.Simon, what are you doing? It's time to leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Do you think we’ll be alone for a few minutes?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiHaOp^.You looked really pretty naked, Ms. Foxx.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AmMaDe.Simon! You know you’re not allowed to look at naked women!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlWoEx^.Someone hit the broadcast button! It wasn’t me! I swear!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.I have an idea of how this happened.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SiWoDe^.Aww, damn it. Why does this always happen to me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeWoEx.Sir! The phones are ringing off the hook and a crowd is starting to form at the door!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlShAg^.Holy shit! The ratings are through the roof! The whole city is watching!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnEx^.Go deal with them, 1Hero. The segment’s canceled.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.I think your stock is probably skyrocketing, too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnOp^.Very funny, you two… I better make some calls.");
